pull all the assets right away.

00:18:39.600 --> 00:18:42.440
So if we could view
AR content as easily

00:18:42.440 --> 00:18:44.945
as we could view images
or video on the web,

00:18:44.945 --> 00:18:46.070
that would be really great.

00:18:48.770 --> 00:18:52.820
