will actually fit in this space.

00:19:08.570 --> 00:19:11.356
And Wayfair responds
with the tables

00:19:11.356 --> 00:19:12.980
that will actually
fit the constraints,

00:19:12.980 --> 00:19:16.520
and is able to place and render
that object all inside the web

00:19:16.520 --> 00:19:18.530
browser.

00:19:18.530 --> 00:19:21.620
So as you think about being
able to discover content

00:19:21.620 --> 00:19:25.340
very easily, we view this
as a really interesting way

00:19:25.340 --> 00:19:28.790
to make it much easier for
people who own 3D assets

00:19:28.790 --> 00:19:32.460
and want to get more
viewers on those 3D assets

00:19:32.460 --> 00:19:34.370
to get users much more
quickly without having

