we created a Google Cardboard
vending machine, that I love,

00:26:25.040 --> 00:26:27.540
to give customers a
take-away VR experience.

00:26:27.540 --> 00:26:29.580
Once again, not
about creating stuff,

00:26:29.580 --> 00:26:33.290
but creating stuff that works.

