This kitchen vignette
is what you typically

00:26:37.470 --> 00:26:39.480
see when you come into
one of our stores.

00:26:39.480 --> 00:26:43.290
Our benchmark is not "what's
the best AR and VR experience."

00:26:43.290 --> 00:26:46.200
