visualize today

00:26:46.200 --> 00:26:47.470
that is decidedly low tech.

00:26:47.470 --> 00:26:49.980
So when we are building
experiences that are so far

00:26:49.980 --> 00:26:52.020
from moved from where
customers know today--

00:26:52.020 --> 00:26:53.550
this kitchen vignette--

00:26:53.550 --> 00:26:55.830
how do we measure
what's working?

