00:30:50.150 --> 00:30:52.160
And a common thread
of all these location

00:30:52.160 --> 00:30:54.079
based AR experiences
you've just seen

00:30:54.079 --> 00:30:56.120
is they're built on top
of the visual positioning

00:30:56.120 --> 00:30:58.100
